quran[7{c,v,t}:
5,83,"jab woh is kalaam ko suntay hain jo rasool par Itra hai to tum dekhte ho ke haq shanasi ke assar se unn ki ankhen aanso-on se tar ho jati hain woh bol uthte hain ke"" parvar-digaar! hum imaan laaye, hamara naam gawahi dainay walon mein likh le """
5,84,"aur woh kehte hain ke"" aakhir kyun nah hum Allah par imaan layein aur jo haq hamaray paas aaya hai ussay kyun nah maan len jabkay hum iss baat ki khwahish rakhtay hain ke hamara rab hamein Saleh logon mein shaamil kere? """
5,85,unn ke iss qoul ki wajah se Allah ne unn ko aisi jannaten ataa kee jin ke neechay nhrin behti hain aur woh un mein hamesha rahen ge yeh jaza hai naik rawayya ikhtiyar karne walon ke liye
5,86,"rahay woh log jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko maan-ne se inkaar kya aur inhen jhtlaya, to woh jahannum ke mustahiq hain"
5,87,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jo pak cheeze Allah ne tumahray liye halal ki hain inhen haraam nah kar lau aur hadd se tajawaz nah karo, Allah ko zayad-ti karne walay sakht napasand hain"
5,88,jo kuch halal o Tayyab rizaq Allah ne tum ko diya hai ussay kha o piyo aur uss khuda ki nafarmani se bachte raho jis par tum imaan laaye ho
5,89,"tum log jo mehmal kasmain kha letay ho unn par Allah girift nahi karta, magar jo kasmain tum jaan boojh kar khatay ho unn par zaroor tum se muwakhza kere ga ( aisi qisam tornay ka ) kaffara yeh hai ke das miskeeno ko woh ost darjay ka khana khilao jo tum apne baal bachon ko khelati ho, ya inhen kapray peh-nao, ya aik ghulam azad karo, aur jo is ki istetat nah rakhta ho woh teen din ke rozay rakhay yeh tumhari qasmon ka kaffara hai jabkay tum qasam kha kar toar do apni qasmon ki hifazat kya karo is terhan Allah apne ehkaam tumahray liye wazeh karta hai shayad ke tum shukar ada karo"
